  <brief_title>A Phase III Study of Civamide Nasal Solution (Zucapsaicin) for the Treatment of Episodic Cluster Headache</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III, Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Group, Multicenter Evaluation of Civamide (Zucapsaicin) Nasal Solution in the Treatment of Episodic Cluster Headache</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Winston Laboratories</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Winston Laboratories</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a 49-day study to evaluate the effectiveness of Intranasal Civamide (Zucapsaicin) in
      the treatment of an episodic cluster headache period compared to placebo (medically inactive
      substance which does not contain any active ingredients).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
